comments.text:
+The Welsh Warlock that's a different thing, since you can't actually sense 
it. What you described is something like the conscious of knowing.
Like, you have a skeleton in your body(most people are creeped out by this, 
i always thought it was cool though);
There is blood flowing in pretty much every inch of your body;
Your eyeballs are an easy to squish ball with liquid inside;
Your hair is actually dead;
Every time you choke you actually have a piece of food inside your air 
tube, and who knows if all gets out by coughing a few times;
You are constantly leaking liquids and gas from your body, which you only 
notice after 2 days of not washing yourself;
Finally: Stand infront of a mirror, open your mouth, raise your tongue and 
look at the bottom of the inside of your mouth. Have fun being disgusted by 
your own mouth for the rest of your life.

Stuff like that
